column5: Baseline product that covers the historical period from 1500 to 2005

The same as LUHa_t1.v1_minicam.v1 but also including land-use changes and transitions from/to urban land
Fractional gridded information on biofuels - The MiniCAM team treats biofuels as herbaceous crops

the same as LUHa.v1_message.v1 but also including land-use changes and transitions from/to urban land
